{"tid":2218148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳智庫研究揭新疆過萬清真寺被毀　外交部否認：造謠污衊","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:26:37.000Z","uid":53379,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"51d7f364526cc3a8b23d0a4bc308d665e79fb1ce","tid":2218148,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">澳智庫研究揭新疆過萬清真寺被毀　外交部否認：造謠污衊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/xj-02_wAGLe_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fxj-02_wAGLe_1200x0.png&h=acbbe590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲智庫、澳大利亞戰略研究所（ASPI）周五發布一份報告，透過分析人造衛星圖片，發現自 2017 年，全新疆有約 16,000 間清真寺被摧毀或損壞，其中一半以上（約 8500 間）遭直接拆除，大部分破壞及清拆是在 2017 年後發生。ASPI 估計，目前新疆清真寺數目是自文革以來最低水平。<br />\n<br />\nASPI 周五（25日）發布一份題為《追踪新疆維吾爾族及伊斯蘭教空間被破壞的的過程》報告，透過對比人造衛星照片，分析新疆各地清真寺及維吾爾族宗教文化遺址在 2017 年前後的狀況，估算有關建築物遭破壞的情況。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/ac-%E6%BE%B3%E6%99%BA%E5%BA%AB%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8F%AD%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86-1-6-%E8%90%AC%E9%96%93%E6%B8%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%80-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D-%E9%80%A0%E8%AC%A0%E6%B1%A1%E8%A1%8A/?fbclid=IwAR05XcUTSWiGC8quUA3D8l2HHvPmVKpB-NObAGHx4IAyy6rprvhhYz5wjzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2Fac-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2596%2586-1-6-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E8%25A1%258A%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR05XcUTSWiGC8quUA3D8l2HHvPmVKpB-NObAGHx4IAyy6rprvhhYz5wjzk&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuyBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=7e53a5ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed